        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_PRO/Scenes/Missions/CoastalTown/_scene_mamba.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 36eab2c5-79b3-4aca-bf8b-8b40ff64c3d5).Image",
        "Description": "Our client lost his heart to a beautiful woman in Sapienza, only for her to reveal that she is a serial killer -  the Honeymoon Harpy. He narrowly escaped with his life, but has made it his mission to end her murderous career. Her crimes could have been stopped years ago If only the priest who took her confession had alerted the police. NOTE: The intended kill condition for the priest is Falling Object, but the bell doesn’t count for whatever reason. Drop it on him if you wish to play along.",
